data.description:
Welcome to this charming one-story home located in the beautiful city of Santa Rosa, CA. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this house offers a comfortable and spacious living environment. 

The remodeled kitchen features a kitchen island and quartz counters, providing a modern and stylish space for all your culinary adventures. The primary bedroom boasts an ensuite bathroom with a walk-in shower, while the carpeted flooring adds a cozy touch. The second bathroom features a shower over tub, perfect for a relaxing soak after a long day. 

Flooring options include vinyl plank from the living room through the kitchen, hardwood in two bedrooms, and tile in the bathrooms and at the entry. 

The fully fenced yard provides a nice space for outdoor activities, and the detached garage and breezeway offer ample storage options. 

RV/boat parking and a dog run are additional conveniences that make this home perfect for those with active lifestyles. 

Located close to shopping, public transportation, restaurants, and parks, this house offers easy access to all the amenities you need. Enjoy the proximity to Spring Lake and highways, making commuting and outdoor activities a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
